annotationA: Cullin 3, isoform F; Ubiquitin-protein transferase activity; ubiquitin protein ligase binding; Belongs to the cullin family
annotationB: Regulatory particle triple-A ATPase 4 (Rpt4) is the 19S proteasomal ATPase, which is a component of the 26S proteosome complex. Rpt4 localizes to the nucleolus and participates in regulating rRNA transcription. Rpt4 physically interacts with the BHD tumor suppressor
